title: MS SQL: Availability Groups
agents: windows
catalog: app/mssql
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the the MSSQL availability groups
 that can be found on the queried MSSQL instances.

 A synchronization state of HEALTHY maps to {OK},
 while a synchronization state of NOT_HEALTHY maps to {CRIT}.

 This check needs the Checkmk mssql.vbs plugin installed in
 the agent. Please refer to the online documentation
 for how to install that plugin.

item:
 The name of the MSSQL availability group.

discovery:
 One service is created for each availability group.
